creator: Michele Lynch
title: Twin Flame Transformation - Navigating the Compulsion and Obsession with your Twin Flame
dc:creator: Michele Lynch
content:
Episode 5:  In this episode, Michele explains psychologically why we exhibit compulsive and obsessive behavior toward our Twin Flames when we aren't with them. She gives insights on how we can heal these patterns and how important this healing work is for all Twin Flames.

Website: https://michelelynchhealing.com/

Listener Support: https://anchor.fm/michele-lynch/support
